  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/2bec1564aefa39413f312fdb05ad1f84.avif?t=1768318073\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras_big/2bec1564aefa39413f312fdb05ad1f84.avif?t=1768318073 width=800 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"As a solo developer, I’ve poured my heart into every detail of Short Snow, striving to create an immersive and challenging experience. From the howling winds to the crunch of snow underfoot, every element has been crafted with care and dedication to bring this frozen wilderness to life.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is up to you how you want to play. Choose your adventure with two distinct game modes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/b139ae6b90e720de20c4c9d5819a0a51.poster.avif?t=1768318073\" width=598 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/b139ae6b90e720de20c4c9d5819a0a51.webm?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/b139ae6b90e720de20c4c9d5819a0a51.mp4?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode:</strong>Discover who you are and learn about the past as you fight to survive. Find your friends and make your way back home while facing various challenges along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival Mode:</strong> Dive into a sandbox of limitless possibilities. With abundant resources and an expanded array of crafting options at your disposal, you are free to shape your own destiny. Build, explore, and conquer the world around you on your terms. Whether you seek to create a thriving settlement or challenge the wild in solitary resilience, your journey is yours to define. Adventure awaits at every turn in this open-ended survival experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/69921f49e55071a79e3588c763b89242.avif?t=1768318073\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras_big/69921f49e55071a79e3588c763b89242.avif?t=1768318073 width=800 height=458 /></span>In Short Snow, a realistic open-world survival experience, you find yourself lost in a vast, snow-covered forest after a harrowing plane crash. With temperatures plummeting and hunger gnawing, you must craft your way to survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic Winter Survival: Manage hunger, thirst, and hypothermia as you navigate the unforgiving wilderness. <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the Wild: Encounter dangerous predators and learn to outsmart or outfight them. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the Mystery: Explore the wreckage and uncover the secrets behind the crash. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you succumb to the elements, or will you conquer the frozen wilderness? The choice is yours.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is up to you how you want to play. Choose your adventure with two distinct game modes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/55ada7e0f2c99ade6c3fb2e52bed2bf2.poster.avif?t=1768318073\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/55ada7e0f2c99ade6c3fb2e52bed2bf2.webm?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/55ada7e0f2c99ade6c3fb2e52bed2bf2.mp4?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/43942e10ad67332305f71fcabe31411c.poster.avif?t=1768318073\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/43942e10ad67332305f71fcabe31411c.webm?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/43942e10ad67332305f71fcabe31411c.mp4?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brave the harsh wilderness and explore the vast, snowy forest. Discover hidden secrets, gather essential resources, and uncover the mysteries of the frozen landscape. Every step in the snow, every rustle in the trees, brings you closer to mastering the unforgiving environment.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/2bec1564aefa39413f312fdb05ad1f84.avif?t=1768318073\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras_big/2bec1564aefa39413f312fdb05ad1f84.avif?t=1768318073 width=800 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"As a solo developer, I’ve poured my heart into every detail of Short Snow, striving to create an immersive and challenging experience. From the howling winds to the crunch of snow underfoot, every element has been crafted with care and dedication to bring this frozen wilderness to life.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is up to you how you want to play. Choose your adventure with two distinct game modes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/b139ae6b90e720de20c4c9d5819a0a51.poster.avif?t=1768318073\" width=598 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/b139ae6b90e720de20c4c9d5819a0a51.webm?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/b139ae6b90e720de20c4c9d5819a0a51.mp4?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode:</strong>Discover who you are and learn about the past as you fight to survive. Find your friends and make your way back home while facing various challenges along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survival Mode:</strong> Dive into a sandbox of limitless possibilities. With abundant resources and an expanded array of crafting options at your disposal, you are free to shape your own destiny. Build, explore, and conquer the world around you on your terms. Whether you seek to create a thriving settlement or challenge the wild in solitary resilience, your journey is yours to define. Adventure awaits at every turn in this open-ended survival experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/69921f49e55071a79e3588c763b89242.avif?t=1768318073\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras_big/69921f49e55071a79e3588c763b89242.avif?t=1768318073 width=800 height=458 /></span>In Short Snow, a realistic open-world survival experience, you find yourself lost in a vast, snow-covered forest after a harrowing plane crash. With temperatures plummeting and hunger gnawing, you must craft your way to survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Authentic Winter Survival: Manage hunger, thirst, and hypothermia as you navigate the unforgiving wilderness. <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the Wild: Encounter dangerous predators and learn to outsmart or outfight them. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the Mystery: Explore the wreckage and uncover the secrets behind the crash. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you succumb to the elements, or will you conquer the frozen wilderness? The choice is yours.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is up to you how you want to play. Choose your adventure with two distinct game modes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/55ada7e0f2c99ade6c3fb2e52bed2bf2.poster.avif?t=1768318073\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/55ada7e0f2c99ade6c3fb2e52bed2bf2.webm?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/55ada7e0f2c99ade6c3fb2e52bed2bf2.mp4?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/43942e10ad67332305f71fcabe31411c.poster.avif?t=1768318073\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/43942e10ad67332305f71fcabe31411c.webm?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054440/extras/43942e10ad67332305f71fcabe31411c.mp4?t=1768318073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brave the harsh wilderness and explore the vast, snowy forest. Discover hidden secrets, gather essential resources, and uncover the mysteries of the frozen landscape. Every step in the snow, every rustle in the trees, brings you closer to mastering the unforgiving environment.</p>",
